                    <span>Overall this is an adequate book for the title.  However, coming from McKinsey folks, then...... hmmm.... The writing is a little sloppy and some of the analysis are not really insights.  There ought to be more daring predictions at the end of the book from the authors...  I suggest the authors to create an updated edition NOW since things are changing so much so fast in the software industry.</span>
                  
