                    <span>if you are in information technology and "get the business", then avoid this book...<p>otherwise, look into it... great true stories on how software companies grow organically and rapidly in a business that has revolutionized the way we work and communicate daily.<p>this book is also very beneficial for cio's just entering the "arena" and are in need of some motivation and direction.<p>enjoy!</span>
                  
